name: Fireflower Sprouts
description:
This one made me think of a tangle of sprouts. The tangled linear structures characteristic of the Physarum-like historical velocity term, where things tend to go along the same routes as previous material which passed through an area. Densities above a certain level are set to emit light here, and the light transport is purely diffusion-based. / @ngutten
